{"tid":591071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11歲女童戰勝白血病 卻不幸遭車撞死","createTime":"2018-03-13T08:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T03:50:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":81,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"b98420ac48921335329902105f895b05067a9484","tid":591071,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpnrSuaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpnrSuaS.jpg&h=e2fdd7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">艾蜜莉在5歲得到白血病，經過2年積極治療終於戰勝病魔，可惜最近卻因車禍而死。（圖擷自《BPM MEDIA》）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕英國英格蘭林肯郡有一名11歲女童艾蜜莉（Amelia Wood），年幼時曾罹患白血病（Leukemia），最後經過積極治療終於成功擊退病魔，卻在上學途中因車禍而不幸命喪黃泉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpejaGNF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpejaGNF.jpg&h=7a3321b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">艾蜜莉平時在學校熱心助人，相當受歡迎（圖擷自《PA》）</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，艾蜜莉在5歲時被診斷出白血病，每週都要到醫院4次，每天都要吃10劑的藥，但艾蜜莉始終很勇敢地接受治療，經過2年多她終於戰勝病魔。本應擁有大好前程，可惜最後仍不敵死神；她在上週二清晨前往上學的路上，意外遭到車輛撞擊，雖然緊急送醫，但最後仍回天乏術。<br />\n<br />\n艾蜜莉學校校長透露，艾蜜莉為人善良且貼心，曾獲選為學校委員會成員，幫助年紀較小的學生；在學校人緣也很好，同時她也是一名優秀的籃網球（Netball）選手。全校師生、朋友接獲消息都感到相當震驚及難過，「大家都會記得這位有活力、熱情又堅定的學生」。<br />\n<br />\n林肯郡警方指出，肇事司機是一名年約20多歲的本地男性，目前也正著手調查車禍情形並還原現場，也呼籲車禍目擊者向警局提供相關線索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2362715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2362715&d=RRFyPJExOFzaatkg3WeVH3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=b245ed91\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2362715&h=f548ff30\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2362715</a>"},{"pid":"ae87c99b0588c3df7a2c55efeb9314d5d1e127ad","tid":591071,"uid":5190,"like":117,"dislike":5,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:22:50.000Z","msg":"如果 命運能選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82071653548c31102085f3edf86758249fb5afed","tid":591071,"uid":97814,"like":3,"dislike":71,"score":-68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b38e1ca63b606d8586f8c94687add67751b555bd","tid":591071,"uid":160579,"like":224,"dislike":3,"score":221,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係命裡有時終需有<br />\nrip"},{"pid":"e077194347d476b52c98d4c92fc26f3f71dd13a6","tid":591071,"uid":43009,"like":39,"dislike":338,"score":-299,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"醫返都嘥藥費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3252256f9ec43dc9996863216c2965dc3c1ea175","tid":591071,"uid":64318,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"80637c699c5c96c9bb0e57cefd1001342ef88ad0","tid":591071,"uid":28378,"like":130,"dislike":14,"score":116,"quote":{"pid":"e077194347d476b52c98d4c92fc26f3f71dd13a6","tid":591071,"uid":43009,"like":39,"dislike":338,"score":-299,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"醫返都嘥藥費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"mean but true, btw rip"},{"pid":"8b65bc9ca93fcfc3d05dc820823e00d520f3c2d2","tid":591071,"uid":94828,"like":346,"dislike":11,"score":335,"quote":{"pid":"e077194347d476b52c98d4c92fc26f3f71dd13a6","tid":591071,"uid":43009,"like":39,"dislike":338,"score":-299,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:31:34.000Z","msg":"醫返都嘥藥費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"你老母醫你個弱智就真係嘥藥費"},{"pid":"2f1e3247988eebfa54ff6deae1b337bdfbee1264","tid":591071,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13